Create Web applications for the Hospitality Industry.
● Create Model HotelBooking.
● Create a migration file to define the schema for the hotel_bookings table.
● Attributes: guestName, checkInDate, checkOutDate, roomType
● Create Controller: HotelBookingController with all method classes.
Create a new Hotel record, display them in tabular format with the action buttons of edit and
delete. Also add a new field button on the right side corner to add a new record.
And on click of delete the record should be deleted and the record should be edited in different
pages.
Note: All fields are required fields. Room type should be in select options and date should
have a date picker.
